metadata.name: Break
metadata.description: The reversal of the obviously integrated principles of perception and emotion creates a new space in which, behind the scenes of life, the subconscious emotions and voices play a major role, and themselves and their impenetrable forms take the form of different things.  Thus, the combined nature of shadows, as a necessary and inevitable element, but inconsistent and eerie, becomes a powerful tool for achieving vague and distorted knowledge that leaves shadows instead of revealing things by breaking the imaginary veil of illusion.  And keeps themselves safe with their secrets and content, perfect and flawless ...
